OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry night
OL,6,Fwith late evening sunshine and largely
OL,7,Fclear skies for Orkney. Shetland will
OL,8,Fstart cloudy but long clear spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping later in the night. Light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA dry day with largely
OL,13,Fclear skies and plenty of sunshine on
OL,14,Foffer. Maybe some patchy high level
OL,15,Fcloud turning sunshine hazy over
OL,16,FShetland. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
