OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fand settled Thursday and Friday with
OL,7,Fvariable cloud and sunny spells. A
OL,8,Fmostly cloudy day on Saturday with
OL,9,Fshowers possible. Breezy on Thursday,
OL,10,Fotherwise light winds.
